      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been reliably maintained. The exterior is well-preserved, showing only minor, age-appropriate surface scratches and small stone chips that do not detract from its overall appeal. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all major features and electronics functioning as intended. It drives smoothly and represents a dependable choice for a buyer seeking a quality pre-owned car without the premium of a showroom-perfect model.",
